OL,3,CFewer phone thefts after drone and e-
OL,4,Cbike tactics used to catch thieves
OL,6,FPolice say phone theft in the capital
OL,7,Fhas dropped after a crackdown which
OL,8,Fused drone and e-bike tactics.
OL,10,FLatest figures show a 21 per cent
OL,11,Freduction in theft from person
OL,12,Foffences across London, meaning 20,000
OL,13,Ffewer victims, according to the Met
OL,14,FPolice.
OL,16,FIn total, 67,064 phone theft offences
OL,17,Fwere recorded in the year ending April
OL,18,F2026.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
