OL,3,CFewer phone thefts after drone and e-
OL,4,Cbike tactics used to catch thieves
OL,6,FThe Met have also seized 3,000
OL,7,Fillegally modified e-bikes and e-
OL,8,Fscooters since January 2025.
OL,10,FAs part of Met Police work on to clamp
OL,11,Fdown on phone theft epidemic on Friday
OL,12,F24 April police arrested six people
OL,13,Ffor robbery.
OL,15,FMet officers targeted crime hotspots
OL,16,Fin south London around Southbank,
OL,17,FBorough Market and Waterloo where
OL,18,Fphone thieves are known to operate.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
