OL,3,CFewer phone thefts after drone and e-
OL,4,Cbike tactics used to catch thieves
OL,6,FPlain clothes officers, identified a
OL,7,Fgroup of suspected phone thieves
OL,8,Foperating on Borough High Street in
OL,9,FSouthwark.
OL,11,FThe suspects were using a distraction
OL,12,Ftactic which involved approaching
OL,13,Fmembers of the public and asking them
OL,14,Fto open their phones to follow them on
OL,15,Fsocial media.
OL,17,FWhile the device was unlocked, they
OL,18,Fwould steal the phone. Officers moved
OL,19,Fin within minutes to intercept the
OL,20,Fgroup, arresting the suspects on
OL,21,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to rob.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
