PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777464667
OL,3,CFewer phone thefts after drone and e-
OL,4,Cbike tactics used to catch thieves
OL,6,FMet Commissioner Sir Mark Rowley has
OL,7,Fcalled on phone manufacturers and
OL,8,Ftechnology companies to do more to
OL,9,Fstop stolen devices being reset and
OL,10,Fresold.
OL,12,FHe has set a deadline of 1 June for
OL,13,Findustry to introduce meaningful
OL,14,Fmeasures to help "design out crime" by
OL,15,Fmaking stolen phones worthless. If
OL,16,Fprogress is not made, the Met will ask
OL,17,Fthe government to consider legislative
OL,18,Faction.
OL,26,@vD@ROUvD@cO]
