OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777464667
OL,3,CFewer phone thefts after drone and e-
OL,4,Cbike tactics used to catch thieves
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Gareth
OL,7,FGilbert, who leads action against
OL,8,Fphone theft in Southwark and Lambeth,
OL,9,Fsaid:
OL,11,F"We are cracking down on phone theft,
OL,12,Fand our tactics are delivering
OL,13,Fresults. Across London, neighbourhood
OL,14,Fcrime is down by more than 15 per
OL,15,Fcent. That's 40,000 fewer victims
OL,16,Fspared the stress, cost and disruption
OL,17,Fof crime.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
