PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777464667
OL,3,CFewer phone thefts after drone and e-
OL,4,Cbike tactics used to catch thieves
OL,6,F"In Southwark and Lambeth, what we are
OL,7,Fdoing is working. In just one week, we
OL,8,Fcut e-bike enabled crime, which is
OL,9,Flinked to phone theft, by nearly 40
OL,10,Fper cent.
OL,12,F"Our message is simple: if you commit
OL,13,Fthese crimes, we will catch you."
